ontent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104aam1665702585156.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/aam1665702585156.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/aam1665702585156.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"aam1665702585156\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      Derived Component Field\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body refbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">A Derived Component Field references a Modeled Field and initially inherits its properties and code containers.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"aam1665702585156__section_e3n_nll_mwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1063753e51\">Characteristics</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"aam1665702585156__table_d10520e1_d10521e1_d10522e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"aam1665702585156__table_d10520e1_d10521e1_d10522e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Characteristics</p>\n</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"aam1665702585156__table_d10520e1_d10521e1_d10522e1__entry__2\"></th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"aam1665702585156__table_d10520e1_d10521e1_d10522e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Icon:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"aam1665702585156__table_d10520e1_d10521e1_d10522e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\"><img alt=\"Icon\" class=\"image\" id=\"aam1665702585156__image_np1_qll_mwb\" src=\"https://docs-be.rocketsoftware.com/bundle/uniface_104/page/component_field_modeled2_c84183a949a6608a6ed22baaba9f9402.png?_LANG=enus\"/></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"aam1665702585156__table_d10520e1_d10521e1_d10522e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Object type code:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"aam1665702585156__table_d10520e1_d10521e1_d10522e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">fld</span>\n</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"aam1665702585156__table_d10520e1_d10521e1_d10522e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Main Development Object?</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"aam1665702585156__table_d10520e1_d10521e1_d10522e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">No</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"aam1665702585156__table_d10520e1_d10521e1_d10522e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Part of:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"aam1665702585156__table_d10520e1_d10521e1_d10522e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"xyt1665703024880.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/xyt1665703024880.html\" title=\"A Derived Component Entity is a Development Object that references and inherits from a Modeled Entity. It has a Component or Modeled Component as parent object. It is used for the component's database I/O, data presentation, and inter-component communication.\">Derived Component Entity</a>\n</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"aam1665702585156__table_d10520e1_d10521e1_d10522e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Contains:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"aam1665702585156__table_d10520e1_d10521e1_d10522e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Value, <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"jgi1665702550212.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/jgi1665702550212.html\" title=\"A Property is a named, typed attribute of Development Object that defines a characteristic or behavior of the object. Each property has a descriptive name, a literal name, a data type, and a value. If no value is specified, a default value may be used.\">Property</a>, <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"cny1665702550298.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/cny1665702550298.html\" title=\"A Code Container is a type of Property that holds code, such as ProcScript, JavaScript, or HTML. It can contain one or more code modules, such as triggers, operations, functions, or entries, or HTML for the layout.\">Code Container</a>\n</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"aam1665702585156__table_d10520e1_d10521e1_d10522e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Generalization:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"aam1665702585156__table_d10520e1_d10521e1_d10522e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"zyj1665702550619.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/zyj1665702550619.html\" title=\"A Component Field is a Development Object that represents a unit of data in a Component Entity.\">Component Field</a>\n</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"aam1665702585156__table_d10520e1_d10521e1_d10522e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Specializations:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"aam1665702585156__table_d10520e1_d10521e1_d10522e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">—</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"aam1665702585156__table_d10520e1_d10521e1_d10522e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Compilation Output</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"aam1665702585156__table_d10520e1_d10521e1_d10522e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">—</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"aam1665702585156__table_d10520e1_d10521e1_d10522e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">URI format:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"aam1665702585156__table_d10520e1_d10521e1_d10522e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">cpt:<var class=\"keyword varname\">ComponentName</var>:ent:<var class=\"keyword varname\">FieldName</var>:fld:<var class=\"keyword varname\">FieldName</var>\n</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"aam1665702585156__section_cvx_qll_mwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1063753e270\">Specialization</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"aam1665702585156__p_d95072e1_d95073e1_d95074e1\">A derived field specializes Component Field in the\n        following ways:</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"aam1665702585156__ul_ayz_rll_mwb\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"aam1665702585156__li_d37436e1_d37437e1_d37438e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"aam1665702585156__p_d95075e1_d95076e1_d95077e1\">It has a derived entity as parent.</p>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"aam1665702585156__li_d37439e1_d37440e1_d37441e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"aam1665702585156__p_d95078e1_d95079e1_d95080e1\">It references a Modeled Field.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3611821\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3611821\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Derived Component Field Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Okt 09, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Derived Component Field A Derived Component Field references a Modeled Field and initially inherits its properties and code containers. Characteristics Characteristics Icon: Object type code: fld Main Development Object? No Part of: Derived Component Entity Contains: Value, Property , Code Container Generalization: Component Field Specializations: — Compilation Output — URI format: cpt: ComponentName :ent: FieldName :fld: FieldName Specialization A derived field specializes Component Field in the following ways: It has a derived entity as parent. It references a Modeled Field. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}